461
00:22:27,637 --> 00:22:30,723
Did you know there's a swimming pool
under this floor?

462
00:22:30,807 --> 00:22:33,017
And did you know
that button behind you

463
00:22:33,101 --> 00:22:35,019
causes this floor to open up?

464
00:22:36,145 --> 00:22:39,399
And did you further know
that George Bailey

465
00:22:39,482 --> 00:22:41,818
