00:24:20,458 --> 00:24:25,004
Of the moon?

478
00:24:25,505 --> 00:24:28,341
- Oh, hot dog. Just like an organ.
- Beautiful.

479
00:24:28,424 --> 00:24:30,635
I told Harry I thought
I'd be bored to death.

480
00:24:30,718 --> 00:24:32,971
You should have seen
the commotion in that locker room.

481
00:24:33,054 --> 00:24:35,807
I had to knock down three people
