484
00:24:39,602 --> 00:24:41,437
I guess
I'm not quite the football type.

485
00:24:41,521 --> 00:24:43,272
You look wonderful!

486
00:24:43,690 --> 00:24:45,024
You know, if it wasn't me talking,

487
00:24:45,108 --> 00:24:46,526
I'd say you were
the prettiest girl in town.

488
00:24:48,277 --> 00:24:50,697
Well, why don't you say it?

489
00:24:50,780 --> 00:24:54,158
I don't know. Maybe I will say it.
How old are you anyway?

490
00:24:55,118 --> 00:24:56,285
Eighteen.

491
00:24:56,369 --> 00:24:59,872
Eighteen? Why, it was only last year
you were seventeen.

492
00:25:00,456 --> 00:25:01,874
Too young or too old?

493
00:25:01,958 --> 00:25:04,711
Oh, no, no. Just right.
Your age fits you.

494
00:25:05,545 --> 00:25:08,256
Yes, sir, you look a little older
without your clothes on.

495
00:25:08,339 --> 00:25:11,718
I mean,
without a dress you look older.

496
00:25:11,801 --> 00:25:14,721
I mean younger.
You look... You just...

