And that goes for you, too!

1362
01:12:41,648 --> 01:12:43,733
And it goes for you, too!

1363
01:12:50,699 --> 01:12:53,743
You wouldn't mind living
in the nicest house in town,

1364
01:12:54,160 --> 01:12:56,788
buying your wife
a lot of fine clothes,

1365
01:12:56,997 --> 01:13:00,542
going to New York on a business trip
a couple of times a year,

1366
01:13:00,625 --> 01:13:02,836
maybe Europe once in a while.

1367
01:13:03,837 --> 01:13:05,922
! know what I'm gonna do tomorrow

1368
01:13:06,006 --> 01:13:09,259
and the next day and next year
and the year after that.

1369
01:13:09,342 --> 01:13:12,470
I'm shaking the dust of this
crummy little town off my feet,

1370
01:13:12,554 --> 01:13:14,389
and I'm gonna see the world.

1371
01:13:14,472 --> 01:13:17,225
And then I'm gonna build things.
I'm gonna build air fields.

1372
01:13:17,309 --> 01:13:19,895
I'm gonna build skyscrapers
100 stories high.

1373
01:13:19,978 --> 01:13:22,105
I'm gonna build a bridge a mile long.

1374
01:13:23,648 --> 01:13:26,818
What is it you want, Mary?
What, you want the moon?

1375
01:13:27,360 --> 01:13:29,821
If you do, just say the word,
I'll throw a lasso around it

1376
01:13:29,905 --> 01:13:31,656
and pull her down for you.

1377
