Mary Hatch,

1383
01:13:59,809 --> 01:14:02,604
why in the world
did you ever marry a guy like me?

1384
01:14:04,064 --> 01:14:06,232
To keep from being an old maid.

1385
01:14:06,733 --> 01:14:08,151
You could have married Sam Wainwright

1386
01:14:08,234 --> 01:14:09,986
and anybody else in town.

1387
01:14:10,362 --> 01:14:13,073
I didn't want
to marry anybody else in town.

1388
01:14:14,115 --> 01:14:16,117
I want my baby to look like you.

1389
01:14:16,242 --> 01:14:18,286
You didn't even have a honeymoon.

1390
01:14:18,370 --> 01:14:19,746
I promised you...

1391
01:14:20,580 --> 01:14:22,874
- Your what?
- My baby.

1392
01:14:25,585 --> 01:14:27,128
Your... Your...

1393
01:14:28,004 --> 01:14:29,714
Mary, you on the nest?

1394
01:14:29,923 --> 01:14:33,885
- George Bailey lassoes stork.
- Lassoes a stork!

1395
01:14:37,889 --> 01:14:41,810
You mean you...
