1399
01:14:54,447 --> 01:14:56,574
Then she had another one, a girl.

1400
01:14:56,825 --> 01:14:58,868
Day after day she worked away,

1401
01:14:58,952 --> 01:15:01,871
remaking the old Granville house
into a home.

1402
01:15:02,080 --> 01:15:05,625
Night after night,
George came back late from the office.

1403
