Commander Harry Bailey!

1442
01:17:12,836 --> 01:17:15,338
Mr. Gower, look at this,
the second page.

1443
01:17:15,421 --> 01:17:16,673
Now, look, this is for you.

1444
01:17:16,756 --> 01:17:18,216
