1690
01:29:56,599 --> 01:29:59,768
- Hey, you! I'll knock your block off!
- What is that?

1691
01:29:59,852 --> 01:30:01,687
Hello! Who's this?

1692
01:30:01,770 --> 01:30:03,314
Oh, Mr. Welch?

1693
01:30:03,689 --> 01:30:05,149
Okay, that's fine, Mr. Welch.

1694
01:30:05,232 --> 01:30:07,276
Give me a chance to tell you
what I really think of your wife.

1695
01:30:07,359 --> 01:30:08,444
George, stop it.

1696
01:30:08,527 --> 01:30:10,237
Will you get out
and let me handle this?

1697
01:30:10,321 --> 01:30:12,865
Hello? Hello? What?

1698
01:30:14,575 --> 01:30:16,118
Oh, you will, huh?

1699
01:30:16,201 --> 01:30:19,121
Okay, Mr. Welch. Any time
you think you're man enough, you...

1700
01:30:19,204 --> 01:30:20,748
Hello! Any...

1701
01:30:24,960 --> 01:30:26,045
Dad, how do you spell "hallelujah"?

1702
01:30:26,128 --> 01:30:28,005
How should I know?
What do you think I am, a dictionary?

1703
01:30:28,088 --> 01:30:29,340
Tommy, stop that! Stop it!

1704
01:30:29,423 --> 01:30:31,300
Janie, haven't you learned
that silly tune yet?

1705
01:30:31,383 --> 01:30:34,386
You play it over and over again.
Now stop it! Stop it!

1706
01:31:02,206 --> 01:31:03,415
I'm sorry, Mary.

1707
01:31:07,086 --> 01:31:09,004
Janie, I'm sorry.

1708
01:31:09,672 --> 01:31:13,509
I didn't mean that. ll...
You go on and practice.

